00:02:06.480 --> 00:02:06.750
STEPHEN COLBERT: I know.

00:02:06.750 --> 00:02:07.460
No, no.

00:02:07.460 --> 00:02:07.870
Go on.

00:02:07.870 --> 00:02:08.490
Go on, please.

00:02:08.490 --> 00:02:11.050
ERIC SCHMIDT: OK. "Which means
we never were not, and thus

00:02:11.050 --> 00:02:11.800
never have been.

00:02:11.800 --> 00:02:14.900
