in trouble.

00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:16.570
Yes?

00:03:16.570 --> 00:03:16.840
OK.

00:03:16.840 --> 00:03:18.780
OK, you can tell because I am
the country, and I'm all

00:03:18.780 --> 00:03:22.330
