then that would mean America

00:03:35.010 --> 00:03:38.020
was never great.

00:03:38.020 --> 00:03:38.480
Right?

00:03:38.480 --> 00:03:39.760
ERIC SCHMIDT: Yes.

00:03:39.760 --> 00:03:43.820
STEPHEN COLBERT: But if I said
that we presently aren't, that

00:03:43.820 --> 00:03:47.350
would mean I am criticizing
America, which you

00:03:47.350 --> 00:03:49.690
mustn't ever do.

00:03:49.690 --> 00:03:53.670
Therefore, it's "America
Again, Re-becoming the

00:03:53.670 --> 00:03:56.460
Greatness We Never Weren't."
Unless you've got something

00:03:56.460 --> 00:03:58.840
