people and YouTube would love

00:04:04.400 --> 00:04:09.220
to know what problem you've got
with the US of A, mister.

00:04:09.220 --> 00:04:09.890
Because I don't.

00:04:09.890 --> 00:04:14.414
And I've proven it with a title
that makes no sense.

00:04:14.414 --> 00:04:15.665
ERIC SCHMIDT: But I
thought you just

00:04:15.665 --> 00:04:16.560
