in the same breath.

00:04:41.310 --> 00:04:42.170
ERIC SCHMIDT: Makes
perfect sense.

00:04:42.170 --> 00:04:42.500
STEPHEN COLBERT: Yeah.

00:04:42.500 --> 00:04:46.040
American exceptionalism means
the rules don't apply to us.

00:04:46.040 --> 00:04:50.680
But the feeling on the right is
that we are losing the game

00:04:50.680 --> 00:04:52.330
