"Very Funny Fellow," David

00:54:05.940 --> 00:54:09.090
Frye, "Richard Nixon, A
Fantasy," George Carlin,

00:54:09.090 --> 00:54:14.310
"Class Clown," "Let's Get
Small," "Wild and Crazy Guy."

00:54:14.310 --> 00:54:17.600
Back when you could stack
albums, stack so many of them,

00:54:17.600 --> 00:54:21.800
the top one kind of played
slow as it went around.

00:54:21.800 --> 00:54:23.830
And then I went to college
to be an actor,

00:54:23.830 --> 00:54:24.780
but an actor actor.

00:54:24.780 --> 00:54:26.173
I wore black, and
I had a beard.

00:54:26.173 --> 00:54:31.250
And I was like, let me share
my misery with you.

00:54:31.250 --> 00:54:33.820
Poet slash jerk kind of actor.

00:54:33.820 --> 00:54:36.550
And then I accidentally met some
people from Second City

00:54:36.550 --> 00:54:38.950
and took some classes there and
got invited to audition

00:54:38.950 --> 00:54:40.150
and accidentally--

00:54:40.150 --> 00:54:41.580
just sort of the happy
accident--

00:54:41.580 --> 00:54:43.860
fell in with some
great people.

00:54:43.860 --> 00:54:47.850
And I quit Second City four
times in order to go do

00:54:47.850 --> 00:54:50.100
straight, black box
avant-garde kind

00:54:50.100 --> 00:54:51.360
of theater in Chicago.

00:54:51.360 --> 00:54:52.170
That's what I was going to be.

00:54:52.170 --> 00:54:54.590
I was going to live in a studio
apartment with no

00:54:54.590 --> 00:54:58.370
furniture and a futon on the
floor that I stuffed myself

00:54:58.370 --> 00:54:59.430
