00:55:06.670 --> 00:55:10.120
And I was going to drink from a
samovar that was constantly

00:55:10.120 --> 00:55:13.000
bubbling in the background.

00:55:13.000 --> 00:55:14.940
But then one day,
I was backstage.

00:55:14.940 --> 00:55:16.640
I kept on returning
to doing comedy.

00:55:16.640 --> 00:55:18.290
And I was backstage one night.

00:55:18.290 --> 00:55:20.460
And this is really the thing
that made the decision for me.

00:55:20.460 --> 00:55:22.090
I was backstage with
a guy named Dave

00:55:22.090 --> 00:55:25.100
Razowsky, who does a--

00:55:27.630 --> 00:55:28.620
