00:56:29.190 --> 00:56:32.590
And we said, it's not
getting any laughs.

00:56:32.590 --> 00:56:34.190
This is foolproof.

00:56:34.190 --> 00:56:35.090
No laughs at all.

00:56:35.090 --> 00:56:35.680
What's going on?

00:56:35.680 --> 00:56:36.910
Something's wrong.

00:56:36.910 --> 00:56:39.140
And then she goes,
oh, I forgot.

00:56:39.140 --> 00:56:40.390
It's song for whales.

00:56:46.890 --> 00:56:50.890
And we burst into laughter
backstage.

00:56:50.890 --> 00:56:54.140
And we threw our arms around
each other in the

00:56:54.140 --> 00:56:58.340
agony of her failure.

00:56:58.340 --> 00:56:59.950
And we're just laughing.

00:56:59.950 --> 00:57:03.240
We fell like a collapsing
tee-pee.

00:57:03.240 --> 00:57:05.190
We just fell to the ground.

00:57:05.190 --> 00:57:09.740
And Dave's feet went out onto
stage, like this, as we held

00:57:09.740 --> 00:57:12.360
