00:57:25.670 --> 00:57:28.960
And I thought at that moment,
this is what I want.

00:57:28.960 --> 00:57:34.970
If failure of this scale can
cause this much joy for

00:57:34.970 --> 00:57:38.100
anyone, then this is the
healthiest thing that I could

00:57:38.100 --> 00:57:39.320
do with the rest of my life.

00:57:39.320 --> 00:57:41.430
And I will do nothing else.

00:57:41.430 --> 00:57:43.510
And I've never looked back
from that moment.

